{"tid":169302,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《碧血狂殺2 Red Dead Redemption 2》","createTime":"2017-03-24T06:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T08:49:19.000Z","uid":18024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fddbadfcdc27ed076995fe06dcb79172c0697c23","tid":169302,"uid":18024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T06:19:12.000Z","msg":"Rockstar 西部荒野大作《碧血狂殺2》發售日遭零售商洩露！<br />\n<br />\n今年玩家們最期待的作品之一想必就是由 Rockstar 所推出的西部開放式世界角色扮演遊戲《碧血狂殺2 Red Dead Redemption 2》了，不過到目前為止，Rockstar 僅表示遊戲將在今年秋季發售，確切的發售日期仍不得而知，然而現在有英國零售商就悄悄地洩露了本作的發售日期，將在 2017 年 9 月 26 日發售。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Red-Dead-Redemption.png?resize=640%2C360&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2FRed-Dead-Redemption.png%3Fresize%3D640%252C360%26ssl%3D1&h=29d841ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國零售商 Base 近日洩露了《碧血狂殺2》的發售日期，將在 9 月 26 日發售，而這不僅符合官方預定的秋季發售日，此外也符合英國 AAA 級大作通常發售的日子&mdash;&mdash;星期二。而該零售商的商店網頁中，其他尚未公布發售日期的遊戲都是以 2017 年 12 月 31 日佔位用日期來標示，因此也讓人猜測該零售商有可能已經取得發售日期的通知。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/rdr2date.png?resize=640%2C193&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2Frdr2date.png%3Fresize%3D640%252C193%26ssl%3D1&h=a6d619b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/03/24/red-dead-redemption-release-date-leaked-by-uk-retailer/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2017%2F03%2F24%2Fred-dead-redemption-release-date-leaked-by-uk-retailer%2F&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=214af26b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/03/24/red-dead-redemption-release-date-leaked-by-uk-retailer/</a>"},{"pid":"68435a5f5cbcb849fbfa5cfba59e8cc8d597a0f2","tid":169302,"uid":18024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T06:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa1ebcd394951121815658d743a0e91d42cc8b8","tid":169302,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T07:43:28.000Z","msg":"荒野大嫖客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947702bae58685405f7c873401f9fa5fc6dbfb54","tid":169302,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:49:19.000Z","msg":"推"}]}